<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="1Sep1940"><font color="red">1 September 1940</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Carola Giedion-Welcker): My son and I applied last week for entry into Switzerland &hellip; On the form to be filled out there was the paragraph, References in Switzerland. I gave the names of Giedion, Vogt, Moser and Schoeck [also Prager] &hellip; As for a material guarantee I asked the Brauchbar firm to give it. It is not strictly necessary for as soon as we are in Switzerland we shall be almost at once financially independent </div>
